<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="cool-down-off">cool down / off</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(使) 变凉；(使) 冷却：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The temperature will cool off in the early evening.
入夜时，气温会变低。</p><footer>2010 北京</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>(使) 冷静；(使) 平静：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Her enthusiasm never cooled down. 
她的热忱从未消退。</p><footer>2013 湖南</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She went for a walk to cool herself down / off.
她出去走走，让自己冷静一下。</p></div></div>